q-1
Which of the following Ansible built-in variable populates the flavour of the operating system?
A-1 ansible_os_family

q-2 Which keyword is used to define a condition in an Ansible playbook?
A-2 when

q-3 As per the given playbook, will Ansible install the vim package on a RedHat based machine?

---
- name: Install package
  hosts: app1
  tasks:
    - name: Install
      package:
        name: vim
        state: present
      when: ansible_os_family != "RedHat"

A-3 No. 
